OL,3,CWork and Pensions Secretary: DWP needs
OL,4,Cto focus on work, not welfare
OL,6,FThe Work and Pensions Secretary will
OL,7,Fset out Labour's ambitions to change
OL,8,Fthe DWP from a "department for
OL,9,Fwelfare" to a "department for work" in
OL,10,Fa speech on Tuesday.
OL,12,FIn the speech in Barnsley, Liz Kendall
OL,13,Fwill lay out plans to tackle economic
OL,14,Finactivity and help the Labour
OL,15,FGovernment meet its long-term ambition
OL,16,Fof reaching 80% employment.
