OL,3,CWork and Pensions Secretary: DWP needs
OL,4,Cto focus on work, not welfare
OL,6,FShe will say that under the
OL,7,FConservatives, the DWP focused almost
OL,8,Fentirely on the benefits system and
OL,9,Fimplementing Universal Credit and that
OL,10,Fnot enough attention was given to
OL,11,Fother issues that determine whether
OL,12,Fpeople can work, such as health,
OL,13,Fskills, childcare and transport.
