OL,3,CWork and Pensions Secretary: DWP needs
OL,4,Cto focus on work, not welfare
OL,6,FShe is expected to say: "Over the last
OL,7,F14 years millions of people have been
OL,8,Fdenied their rightful chance of
OL,9,Fparticipating in the labour market,
OL,10,Fand the hope of a brighter future.
OL,11,FThey've been excluded, left out,
OL,12,Fcategorised and labelled. Britain
OL,13,Fisn't working.
OL,15,F"We need fundamental reform so the
OL,16,Fdepartment for welfare becomes a
OL,17,Fgenuine department for work."
OL,19,FLocal leaders will be able to tailor
OL,20,Fschemes to get people back into work
OL,21,Funder the plans.
