OL,3,CWork and Pensions Secretary: DWP needs
OL,4,Cto focus on work, not welfare
OL,6,F"We will give local places the
OL,7,Fresponsibility and resources to design
OL,8,Fa joined-up work, health and skills
OL,9,Foffer that's right for local people.
OL,11,F"DWP will support local areas to make
OL,12,Fa success of this new approach.
OL,14,F"And we will devolve new powers over
OL,15,Femployment support to catalyse action
OL,16,Fand change."
