OL,3,CWork and Pensions Secretary: DWP needs
OL,4,Cto focus on work, not welfare
OL,6,FMs Kendall will announce the Labour
OL,7,FMarket Advisory Board, a group of
OL,8,Fexternal experts to give market
OL,9,Finsight and advice to the DWP and
OL,10,Fchallenge its plans.
OL,12,FThe Work and Pensions Secretary
OL,13,Fpreviously announced that the
OL,14,FGovernment will publish a White Paper
OL,15,Fthat builds on Labour's approach to
OL,16,Fget people working by creating a new
OL,17,Fnational careers service, creating new
OL,18,Fwork, health and skills plans for the
OL,19,Feconomically inactive and with a youth
OL,20,Fguarantee for 18 to 21-year-olds.
