OL,6,FOn Monday, Prime Minister Sir Keir
OL,7,FStarmer said he would be setting up a
OL,8,Fnew body, Skills England, to "fire up"
OL,9,Fthe training of more British workers
OL,10,Fand reduce reliance on foreign labour.
